audit.description: Lists all user links on an account or property, including implicit ones that come from effective permissions granted by groups or organization admin roles. If a returned user link does not have direct permissions, they cannot be removed from the account or property directly with the DeleteUserLink command. They have to be removed from the group/etc that gives them permissions, which is currently only usable/discoverable in the GA or GMP UIs.
